data.message: You can work there as an OT?

message:
Hey Cru :) Looking for a FUN job near the U of M that will work around your class schedule? ACR Homes is HIRING direct care professionals! See for yourself how incredible this company is, and how their VALUES impact the quality of care for the residents and the satisfaction of employees. I worked for ACR Homes during my Kinesiology undergrad, Occupational Therapy grad program, and I continue to work for them even after obtaining an OT position because I love this company! 
Email me to get more info, ask questions, or apply! osbo0206@umn.edu
